{"tid":2260304,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大公司人事問題請教 救命","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T05:39:40.000Z","uid":35330,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"16cdd401772705f65d55a1385fe3fefa3b3441a3","tid":2260304,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n最近入左間公司到做左無耐<br />\n之前已經知道我上司(Manager)同佢上司(Director)非常唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nManager做嘢點到即止 準時收工 做左好耐亦唔打算升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDirector就係鍾意返工做野個類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題就嚟喇 最近有個細project要跟<br />\nManager一早已經講明佢唔會跟 <br />\n亦都得到老闆同意<br />\nDirector就襯Manager放假 <br />\n過嚟搵我拍哂膊頭叫我幫手hold個project<br />\n我已經表明我新入無耐乜柒都唔識 同埋應該等我Manager返嚟先決定好啲<br />\nDirector就即刻板起塊面話依到只係小小野 唔明就教到你明 <br />\n而家唔可以因為一個人唔係到就停左依邊既工作<br />\n<br />\n咁我咪焗住聽佢講同開左小小頭<br />\n中間已經一路wtsapp話俾Manager聽Director搵我做 我已經係咁推都唔得<br />\n<br />\n點知講講下 Manager 就彈左句&ldquo;以後有咩唔明咪搵Director教你囉 我教唔嚟架&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n屌 我即刻嚇死 係咁哂冧<br />\n但係都變得好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下可以點樣處理呀呀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：Director就嚟會調走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a5ecf48ffc67ae34d0f0e9e9fbf7ca76207454","tid":2260304,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280bea6a4b13c029d8be50f80f9c5c8046ad5ba1","tid":2260304,"uid":36952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:40.00